Land Money
Titles protected by Grace of the King.
Each title protected by guardianship of all titles.
Each title is provided with the stamp of the King.

Each individual protects all other individuals with records of proof.
Ancestral Temples on family land have a record of every family’s parcel.
A physical map Ancestral Land kept as a record. 
New maps of Ancestral Land will be added to each repository.

A portion of the family residential parcel is committed to a 20 meter space set as the Ancestral Temple.
Ancestral Temple space may not be sold off, and if all members of the family are gone then the shrine will be damned a graveyard of bad energy, never to be reappropriated by society.

Individual has supreme dominion of the land.
No taxation or forced sale of land.
Land transfers down a public lineage.
Public boundaries, clear lines of ownership, One Ring involvement work to settle all land disputes.

A portion of the land is split into common stock which is used for commerce.
In each 10 Year Cycle 5% maximum of land may be set into the title of common stock.
Repurchase of common stock by owner is set to 110% of sale-price. 
Common stock gives no rights to the holder, it only gives the ability to trade.
This setup favors the family to build upon the land to one-day reclaim at a set-rate of the original purchase.

A portion of land may be sectioned as heir-stock and can be sold at any price.
The Original Ancestral Family must have a standard plot size adjacent to the Ancestral Shrine to allow a sale of heir-stock. 
Heir-stock is the only stock that can evolve into ownership and then Ancestral Land. 
If an individual accumulates a standard parcel size of heir-stock then this can be submitted as a bid to claim as family land in the next 10 Year Cycle. 
Land remains under the domino of the owner until the land bid is ratified by the 10 Year Cycle.
Heir-stock is a public exchange and heir-stock can not be traded. 
Owners of heir-stock can not be coerced to sell back. 
Heir-stock is heavily inspected for validity or coercion. 
After heir-stock converted to family land, the parcel may be submitted in a evaluation for an Ancestral Bid, after the third cyclic period.
Land ownership must be stable and as static as possible to reduce land disputes.

Global assessment audits value of all land  to establish stable global markets.
Assessment revalues the stock value of the land into One Ring.

Land owners converge to land betterment.
Land is the public holding of international wealth.
International metrics establish a clear path to valuation.
Land is worshiped and is the center of value.

Land money is immune to inflation by proper audits. 
Yet, it has a natural growth without disrupting the stability of the system.
Land is a finite resource that also has intrinsic value.
Land money is entirely contained and explicitly calculable. 
The value can be estimated from satellite to the naked eye of a bypasser.

Anti-inflationary nature of Land Money gives high value to 10% returns of common stock. 
{ no taxes, no fees, no devaluation by inflation, finite resource, external assess, no monopoly }

